        public static boolean isAncestor(PsiElement ancestor,
                                 PsiElement element,
                                 boolean strict)
        Checks whether one element in the psi tree is under another.
        Parameters:
        ancestor - parent candidate. false will be returned if ancestor is null.
        element - child candidate
        strict - whether return true if ancestor and parent are the same.
        Returns:
        true if element has ancestor as its parent somewhere in the hierarchy and false otherwise.
